<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>GuardRail - Compliance Management for Medical & Legal Practices</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-primary: #1E293B;
      --color-primary-light: #334155;
      --color-success: #10B981;
      --color-white: #FFFFFF;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F172A 0%, #1E293B 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: var(--color-white);
    }
    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 2rem; }
    header {
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--color-white);
      text-decoration: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .logo-icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      background: var(--color-success);
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    nav a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--color-white); }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--color-success);
      color: var(--color-white);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #059669;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--color-white);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    }
    .hero {
      padding: 6rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--color-success); }
    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    .hero-buttons { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; }
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .feature {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: var(--color-success);
      border-radius: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .feature h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .feature p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.95rem; }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .features { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
        GuardRail
      </a>
      <nav>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
        <%= link_to 'Sign In', new_user_session_path %>
        <%= link_to 'Get Started', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
      </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
      <h1>Never Miss a <span>Compliance Deadline</span> Again</h1>
      <p>GuardRail keeps your medical practice or law firm compliant with automated tracking, smart reminders, and one-click audit reports.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <%= link_to 'Start Free Trial', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-primary' %>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="features" id="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">üîí</div>
        <h3>Compliance Vault</h3>
        <p>Secure storage for HIPAA BAAs, state licenses, insurance policies, and certifications with PDF preview.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">‚è∞</div>
        <h3>Smart Reminders</h3>
        <p>Multi-channel alerts via Email, SMS, and Slack at 90, 60, 30, and 7-day intervals before any deadline.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="feature-icon">üìã</div>
        <h3>Audit-Ready Reports</h3>
        <p>Generate one-click compliance reports to prove to inspectors that all staff certifications are current.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
